        <h3 style="margin:0 0 0 30px">Sun Daily Assignment</h3>
        <p class="paragraph">This was my first ever Flash project. It was supposed to be an interactive animation with two buttons you could use to make the sun rise then set manually. I never figured out how to make it work but I did make some nice visuals, and I at least animated the sun's movement despite not being interactive.</p>
